## 🏗️ System Architecture

### Backend Stack
```
Node.js 18+ + Express
├── PostgreSQL 14+ (with PostGIS for geospatial)
├── Redis 6+ (OTP storage, caching)
├── Socket.io (real-time updates - configured but not used yet)
├── Firebase Admin (phone auth verification)
└── JWT (API authentication)
