```
React Native (Expo SDK 54) + TypeScript
├── React Navigation 6 (bottom tabs + stack)
├── AsyncStorage (token persistence)
├── Axios (API client)
├── Context API (auth, ride, user state)
└── React Native Maps (to be integrated)
```

