POST /api/v1/auth/verify-otp       ✅ Verifies OTP, returns JWT + user
GET  /api/v1/users/me              ✅ Get current user (protected)
PATCH /api/v1/users/me             ✅ Update profile
POST /api/v1/pilot/location        ✅ Update pilot location (PostGIS)
GET  /api/v1/pilot/nearby          ✅ Find nearby pilots (geospatial)
POST /api/v1/rides/notify          ✅ Create ride request
GET  /api/v1/rides/:id             ✅ Get ride details
PATCH /api/v1/rides/:id/start      ✅ Start ride
PATCH /api/v1/rides/:id/end        ✅ End ride
```

**Important Notes:**
- OTP is hardcoded to `123456` in development (see `authController.js`)
- Proximity service is commented out in `server.js` (has schema mismatch)
- CORS is configured for `192.168.1.207:*` (backend IP)
- Redis used for OTP storage (5 min TTL)
- JWT tokens valid for 7 days

