**Auth Flow (FULLY WORKING):**
```
1. User enters phone (10 digits)
2. Frontend calls POST /auth/send-otp
3. Backend stores OTP in Redis, returns success
4. User enters OTP (123456 in dev)
5. Frontend calls POST /auth/verify-otp
6. Backend verifies, creates/finds user, returns JWT
7. Frontend stores JWT, sets user in context
8. User navigates to main app (Map/Tokens/Profile tabs)
```

