## 📚 Additional Context

### Token Economics
- Base reward: 10 tokens per verified ride
- Distance bonus: +5 tokens if >10km
- Streak bonus: +10 tokens after 5 rides in 7 days
- Subscription multiplier: 1.25x for Premium users
- Redemption: 100 tokens ≈ ₹100 voucher value

### User Roles
- **Rider:** Requests rides, earns tokens
- **Pilot:** Offers rides, earns tokens (more)
- **Both:** Can switch roles (future feature)

### Safety Features (Not Implemented Yet)
- KYC verification for pilots
- Live location sharing with emergency contacts
- SOS button
- Trip verification (GPS-based fraud detection)
- Rating system with trust score

